Package: RunATAC
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Importing, Processing, Analyzing, Plotting and Reformatting
    ATAC-seq Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sam Buckberry
Maintainer: Sam Buckberry <sambuckberry@gmail.com>
Description: RunATAC contains functions for importing aligned ATAC-seq data,
    performing QC, generating plots, low-level analyses, and exporting data in a
    wide variety of formats.
